codex
To keep the package buildable without changing manifests, I’m replacing the direct `roko_core` import with a typed singleton registry. Callers that can name `roko_core::RuntimeEvent` still get a process-local `EventBus<roko_core::RuntimeEvent>`, while `roko-runtime` avoids a direct cyclic dependency.
